  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_06_ih_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="7" class="is_star2" lang="y">가로가 4.5 m, 세로가 3.5 m인 직사각형 모양의 꽃밭이 있습니다. 이 꽃밭의 가로와 세로를 각각 1.2배씩 늘여 새로운 꽃밭을 만들려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page">
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="question_box">
              <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA524_06_IH/0007_img.png" alt="" /></div>
              <div class="flex dir_col gap_20">
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  가로 (
                  <div class="input_wrap top">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="5.4"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  )m
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  세로 (
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4.2"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  )m
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(새로운 꽃밭의 가로)=4.5×1.2=5.4 (m)(새로운 꽃밭의 세로)=3.5×1.2=4.2 (m)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page">
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="question_box">
              <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA524_06_IH/0007_img.png" alt="" /></div>
              <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                (
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="22.68"></math-field>
                </div>
                )㎡
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(새로운 꽃밭의 넓이)=5.4×4.2=22.68 (㎡)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
